Package: EpigeneticAgePipeline
Type: Package
Title: Package designed for processing and analyzing DNA methylation data.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stanislav Rayevskiy
Maintainer: srayevsk@uwo.ca
Description: 'EpigeneticAgePipeline' is a comprehensive package designed for processing and analyzing DNA methylation data.
    The package provides a variety of epigenetic age measures, epigenetic age acceleration measures, residual generation, cell-count generation and provides a set of plots and tables used for further analysis.
